      <title>日本的股票下降，野生美国及时的波动率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/japan-s-stocks-set-to-resume-drop-in-wake-of-wild-us-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华尔街上的野外摆动，日本股票在美国贸易关税的全面实施之前削弱了投资者的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/japan-s-stocks-set-to-resume-drop-in-wake-of-wild-us-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
